data.description: Beautiful 3/2 split plan family home with soaring ceilings, crown molding and tray ceiling details in the peaceful neighborhood of Rolling Hills. The fenced back yard is surrounded by an abundance of trees. This traditional home boasts solid wood kitchen cabinets, granite kitchen counter and island bar top. Large family room and living room overlooks covered, screened in lanai. All main rooms have sliding doors opening to the Lanai. The master bedroom has a walk in closet plus two other regular closets. Lots of storage in this home. Half bath located off of the lanai. Separate formal dining room, and casual dining area. Large laundry room next to the kitchen, and extra bonus workshop in the two car garage for hobbies, cottage business or extra storage. Garage is side entry. This home is conveniently located, 10 minutes from World Equestrian Center, 15 minutes to Ocala Airport and an easy drive to Rainbow Springs State Park. Located just three lots off main paved road.
